<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Your Order is Confirmed!</h1>
    <p>
      You have successfully placed your order for:
      <% @order.grouped_line_items.each do |product, line_items| %>
        <li>
          <%= line_items.size %> <%= product.name %>
        </li>
      <% end %>
      <br>
    </p>
    <p>As Always, "Your friendship tastes delicous!"</p>
  </body>
</html>
